```text
seed = seed * 0x19660d + 0x3c6ef35f
decoded_utf16 = encoded_word ^ (((seed & 0xffff) * 2 + 0x11) & 0xffff)
```

The entry target at `0x10052841` initializes context, calls `0x10052a81`, and if that returns null builds the decoded status string:

```text
