- `0x10052cd8`: words `2ab9 8f70 29a4 b975` decode to `bak\x00`
- `0x10052d69`: words `2abf 8f73 29cf` decode to `db\x00`
- `0x10052e01`: words `2ab9 8f78 29a1 b975` decode to `bin\x00`
- `0x10052e92`: words `2abf 8f70 29bb b975` decode to `dat\x00`
